These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
House: modern, cottage, palace, ranch-style
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, february, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the modern house is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| House    | cottage  | ranch-style | palace    | modern       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Birthday   | july   | february | june | november        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, sprite, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, classical, metal
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of funk is the fisherman##1
6. the fan of metal is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Beverage        | sprite   | soy-milk | juice     | mirinda      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | house    | metal   | classical     | funk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
House: modern, craftsman, wooden, gothic-revival
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, 7up, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the modern house is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| House         | modern | craftsman | wooden | gothic-revival |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | sprite    | water | 7up     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

