.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, baking, fishing, board-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, hot-chocolate, fanta
1. the freelancer is the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Hobby       | baking     | board-games      | filmmaking     | fishing      |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk         | fanta      | hot-chocolate        |

