.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil, begonia, balloon-flower
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog, lizard
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Flower   | begonia  | sunflower        | balloon-flower  | daffodil       |
| Pet         | chinchilla | hedgehog    | fish | lizard |

