.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kiwi, cucumber, apple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, baccarat, montecristo, bongani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the person eating artichoke is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person eating apple##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
6. the montecristo-smoker is the person eating cucumber##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
8. the person eating apple is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food           | kiwi | cucumber | apple | artichoke |
| Cigar   | bongani   | montecristo  | baccarat | havana   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

