.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lemon, onion, raspberry
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, december, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, davidoff, aristoff, baccarat
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is the person eating onion##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit  | raspberry | onion   | lemon     |
| Birthday         | july | march   | november  | december |
| Cigar   | aristoff         | dannemann  | davidoff | baccarat  |

