.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: rat, frog, cat, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, tram, taxi
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
6. the person driving the taxi is the person drinking juice##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet   | goldfish  | rat | cat       | frog    |
| Transport   | motorbike   | taxi | jet-ski    | tram |

