.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, zombie, comedy, scientific
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, drawing, traveling, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | comedy        | scientific   | zombie  | fantasy   |
| Hobby   | reading         | chess     | drawing    | traveling       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

