.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, american, argentine, australian
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, golf, skiing, climbing
1. the australian is the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the argentine is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | american    | argentine | australian | turkish        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Sport        | golf    | skiing   | climbing  | rowing |

