.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, photographer, social-worker, videographer
City: san-francisco, london, colone, paris
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, writing, traveling, photography
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
8. the person traveling to colone is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | bartender  | videographer | photographer  | social-worker |
| City       | colone | london        | paris | san-francisco       |
| Hobby   | cooking   | writing          | photography          | traveling       |

