3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the analyst is the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | software-developer   | scientist   | analyst | mechanic |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Pet   | mouse     | horse  | bird  | cat  |

