2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Flower         | begonia | sunflower    | daisy        | marigold |
| Color   | light-blue     | coral     | fuchsia        | black   |
| Sport         | sailing   | lacrosse | skateboarding | skiing  |

