4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
