3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the futuristic house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the van##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the art-deco house##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching comedy movies##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
