.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cranberry, orange
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, water, soy-milk
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, backgammon, bridge
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person eating artichoke is the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person drinking water is the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | apple     | orange   | cranberry | artichoke |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | soy-milk | water | juice   |
| Game           | bridge    | monopoly     | go      | backgammon     |

