4. the person driving the scooter is the chinese##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the mexican##1
7. the french is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Sport           | cricket  | snowboarding | ice-hockey  | cycling |
| Transport   | scooter    | train       | taxi | subway      |
| Nationality   | chinese | canadian  | mexican    | french    |

