.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, musical, animation, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dannemann, cain, old-henry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, parkour, tennis
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
8. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Movie-Genre           | musical  | animation  | romance | thriller |
| Cigar   | old-henry   | davidoff | dannemann   | cain      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 